Protocol: PhotoFolder

Types:  
    Agent A,B,P;
    Data photoFolder;
    Function pk, photos;

Knowledge:
    A:   A,B,P,pk(A),inv(pk(A)),pk(B),pk(P),photoFolder;
    P:   A,B,P,pk(A),pk(B),pk(P),inv(pk(P));
    B:   A,B,P,pk(A),pk(B),pk(P),inv(pk(B)),photoFolder,photos(A);

    where A!=B, A!=P, B!=P

Actions:

A  ->  P  : {{ P, B }inv(pk(A))}pk(P) 

P  ->  A  : { P, B }pk(A)

A  ->  B  : {{ B, P, photoFolder, A }inv(pk(A))}pk(B)

B  ->  P  : {photos(A)}pk(P)

Goals:

B authenticates A on P,B,photoFolder